headline: Keurig Dr Pepper to Report Fourth Quarter 2025 Results and Host Conference Call
summary: Keurig Dr Pepper Inc. (NASDAQ: KDP) will release its financial results for the fourth quarter and full year ended December 31, 2025 before the market opens on Tuesday, February 24, 2026. The Company will also hold a conference call on Tuesday, February 24, 2026 at 8:00 AM (ET) to discuss the results, which will be hosted by Tim Cofer, Chief Executive Officer, and Anthony DiSilvestro, Chief Financial Officer.

headline: Peet’s Coffee to close several San Francisco Bay Area stores this month
summary: Approximately 30 cafés are expected to close across Peet’s network of 183 Bay Area locations.
